<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>CSS Portal - Layout</title>
<!--[if IE]><script src="http://html5shiv.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script><![endif]-->
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/sample.css" />
<title>Toroidal Chess</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/chessboard-0.3.0.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/board.css">

<link href = "https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.4/themes/ui-lightness/jquery-ui.css" rel = "stylesheet">
<script src = "https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.10.2.js"></script>
<script src = "https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.4/jquery-ui.js"></script>

<!--
<link href = "css/jquery-ui.css" rel = "stylesheet">
<script src = "js/jquery-1.10.2.js"></script>
<script src = "js/jquery-ui.js"></script>
-->
<script src="js/chessboard-0.3.0.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="wrapper">
        <div id="leftcolumn">
            <p>USE THIS SPACE TO IMPLEMENT MOVE HISTORY IN THE FUTURE.
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
              Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam.
              Sed nisi. Nulla quis sem at nibh elementum imperdiet. Duis
              sagittis ipsum. Praesent mauris. Fusce nec tellus sed augue semper
              porta. Mauris massa. Vestibulum lacinia arcu eget nulla.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="content">

          <h1 id="vs"> <span id="myName"><%= myName %></span> vs. <span id="enemyName"><%= enemyName %></span></h1>

          <div id="board_buttons">
            <div id="showValid<%= showValid %>"></div>
            <div id="showThreat<%= showThreat %>"></div>
            <div id='<%= roomNamer %>'></div>
            <div id="promotionBox"> <div id="promotionText"> </div> </div>
            <div id="resignBox"> <div id="resignText"> </div> </div>
            <div id="drawBox"> <div id="drawText"> </div> </div>
            <div id="enemyNameDisplay" class="highlightedPlayerName"><%= enemyName %></div>
            <div id="board1"></div>
            <div id="myNameDisplay" class="highlightedPlayerName"><%= myName %></div>
            <div id="buttons">
                <button class="gameButtons" id="resign"> Resign </button>
                <button class="gameButtons" id="draw"> Propose Draw </button>
                <button class="gameButtons" id="return"> Return To Lobby </button>
            </div>
          </div>

       </div>
        <div id="rightcolumn">
          <div id="chatContainer">
            <ul id="messages"></ul>
            <form id="messageForm" action="">
              <input id="m" autocomplete="off" /><button id="chatButton">Send</button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script src="js/board.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
